steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitdash002" and Comment "Testing"
When I add new column with Name "jitdashcol002" Type "integer" for Table name "jitdash002"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash002" displayed in dashboard list
When I select table Name "jitdash002" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "1"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "2"
When I select multi dropdown label "Order by" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002" by value "jitdash002s.jitdashcol002"
